{
  "id": "adv_event_2304_01_01",
  "title": "祭典への参加",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "本日は新たなBIG4として大注目を集めています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ as the new BIG4‚ receiving attention‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "サニーピースにお越しいただいております！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace has joined us today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4333333333,
      "endTime": 8.6999999046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "よろしくお願いしま～す！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice to meet you~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.913333257,
      "endTime": 11.266666666699999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.6466432806
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "元気のいい挨拶、ありがとうございまーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for the energetic greeting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6466432806,
      "endTime": 15.306144404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.602992741
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.9394778486
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "本日はサニピの皆さんとたっぷりトークをして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ we'll have plenty of talks with Sunny Peace‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9394778486,
      "endTime": 20.702992741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "最後は楽曲を披露していただきます！　お楽しみに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and they'll also perform their songs at the end!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.702992741,
      "endTime": 24.9728114363,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3089.3877984000005
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.6661443308,
      "endTime": 29.157300837300003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、お疲れ様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ good work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3573008492,
      "endTime": 31.6923801579,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、この間収録した番組……もう放送されてるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ the show we recorded earlier… It's already airing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0578242494,
      "endTime": 38.0070304109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "さくら……前よりずっとトークが自然に出来てる\n肩の力が抜けてるっていうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura… you're talking much more naturally than before.\nIt feels like you've relaxed more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2203637157,
      "endTime": 46.0257134912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そう……なのかな。えへへ、ありがとう\nこういう番組に何度も出てるうちに慣れてきたのかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R…Really? Maybe I have. Hehe‚ thanks.\nMaybe I've gotten used to these kinds of shows after appearing on them so many times.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.1556224857,
      "endTime": 55.8144634281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "本当に凄いと思う\n私は……まだまだ緊張しちゃうから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really admire that.\nI still get nervous…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.0011299803,
      "endTime": 63.2098600104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、琴乃ちゃん――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Kotono-chan――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.4165265436,
      "endTime": 65.4590468245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんに琴乃ちゃん。先に来てたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan‚ Kotono-chan. You're here first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.5964384193,
      "endTime": 69.0874133701,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 429.27507189999403
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "月ストとサニピ、十人全員揃いましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace‚ everyone's here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.2874134178,
      "endTime": 73.0521072025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんから話があるって\n聞いたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{I heard {user}-san said\nthere's something to discuss…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2654405549,
      "endTime": 76.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "二グループを招集するということは\nきっと重要な用事……のはず",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Calling both groups together…\nIt must be something important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1153291023,
      "endTime": 83.85419524070001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "さくら。さっき、何か言いかけてなかった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ didn't you start saying something earlier?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.0608619646,
      "endTime": 88.1957599596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "……ううん、なんでもないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ it's nothing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3957600073,
      "endTime": 90.8585944132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな揃ったな。仕事やレッスンで忙しい中\n集まってくれてありがとう。早速本題なんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone's here. Thank you for gathering despite\nbeing busy with work and lessons. Let's get straight to the point…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0719276941,
      "endTime": 98.6540140665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今度、NEXT VENUSグランプリ歴代優勝者が\n集まる祭典が開かれることになったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ there's going to be a festival where the past winners of\nthe NEXT VENUS Grand Prix will gather.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.8673474189,
      "endTime": 104.9484586593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……凄いイベントですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… What an amazing event!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.1351252116,
      "endTime": 108.80136094459999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "歴代優勝者って言うと、あのグループとあのグループ\nあ、あとあのグループも……激熱……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you say past winners‚ that group and that group‚\noh‚ and that group too… It's amazing…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0080275731,
      "endTime": 117.38977367449999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、同時優勝をした月ストとサニピにも\n出演のオファーが来たんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And so‚ both Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace‚ who won\nsimultaneously‚ have received an offer to appear in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5764402268,
      "endTime": 122.4674608108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "月ストとサニピは別々で歌うんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace going to perform separately?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.6807942586,
      "endTime": 125.8518827634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そこが悩みどころだったんだが……グランプリの\n決勝では月ストとサニピが十人で歌っただろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what I've been grappling with… But during the Grand Prix finals‚\nMoon Tempest and Sunny Peace performed together with ten people‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.0652161159,
      "endTime": 133.4366220035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "主催者サイドも「十人でのパフォーマンスを\n観られたらとても嬉しい」と話していたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The organizers also said they'd be delighted to\nsee a performance with all ten members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.6499553559,
      "endTime": 139.873651397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……あの感動のステージをふたたび、って\n感じかしらね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… It's like to relive\nthat emotional stage again…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.0736514924,
      "endTime": 146.2097964166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "とても感慨深いですね。これはしっかり準備しないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's very moving. We need to prepare properly for this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.489795323,
      "endTime": 151.3063277084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
